    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"just being\" thing doesnt actually happen in the real world. if i stop performing, people get uncomfortable or they leave. it feels like i'm just stuck in this loop of being tired and alone. it's like there's no version of my life where i actually feel at peace.",
